data.description: Beautiful, centrally-located row home near many restaurants, walkscore of 93! High ceilings, open floorplan, lots of natural light from large windows & skylights. Hardwoods, gas fireplace. Beautiful kitchen w/loads of cabinets, large island, pantry, gas range, stainless appliances. Spacious, private, partially covered deck with storage closet. Custom bathrooms, one with large tiled walk-in shower. Large 2 car garage, plantation shutters, A/C. Lots of storage! Lower level storage or workout room [Home Energy Score = 7. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10004557]
